---
// Closing invitation — white band between the dark modules section and the dark footer.
// Acts as a clear directional link to the first module, not a marketing CTA.
---

<section class="relative bg-canvas border-y border-line overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 grid-lines-light opacity-70 [mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse_at_center,black_20%,transparent_75%)]"></div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-[1360px] px-6 lg:px-10 py-24 lg:py-32">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
      <span class="mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-mute">módulo 00</span>
      <span class="h-px w-12 bg-line"></span>
      <span class="eyebrow text-ink/70 text-[15px]">por onde começar</span>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_1fr] gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-end">
      <h2 class="font-display text-[clamp(3rem,9vw,8rem)] leading-[0.92] font-medium tracking-[-0.04em] text-ink max-w-[14ch]">
        Vamos
        <span class="font-serif italic font-normal tracking-[-0.02em]" style="font-family: var(--font-serif);">
          começar?
        </span>
      </h2>

      <div class="lg:pb-6">
        <p class="text-[15.5px] leading-[1.6] text-ink/70 max-w-[44ch]">
          A introdução apresenta a estrutura do curso, o que cada módulo cobre e a ordem em que as peças se encaixam — antes de qualquer código.
        </p>

        <a
          href="/introducao/bem-vindo"
          class="group mt-8 inline-flex items-center gap-4 rounded-full bg-ink text-canvas pl-4 pr-2 py-2 transition-transform hover:translate-x-1"
        >
          <span class="mono text-[10.5px] tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-canvas/60">
            00
          </span>
          <span class="text-[14.5px] font-medium">
            Bem-vindo ao curso
          </span>
          <span
            class="flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-canvas text-ink transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:rotate-[-45deg]"
          >
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
